game.name: Princess Winter Fashion
game.description:
Your favorite two gorgeous princesses Aurora and Snow White are enjoying their holiday in Paris these days. Suddenly, they have decided to give them a complete makeover and dress them up as per the fashion popular in the city. But the two cute princesses are new to the city so they need your assistance to get the job done. Join Aurora And Snow White Winter Fashion game and be prepared to guide them to have a fashion blast in the winter season at Paris! Keep shopping with them until you create the awesome looks for the twos!
Hey ladies! They are already very excited for their new looks so try to be fast to help them choose the perfect outfits for the season in this brand new girls game. Begin with Snow White by providing her with the needful make-up! Choose a bold purple lipstick, a pale blush, and a matte look with purple and pink eye shadow for the girl! Dress her up with a pair of black color paints and combine it with a yellow blouse and a beautiful long blue trench coat and a lovely pair of yellow ear muffs in this HTML5 dressing game!

Hurry up girls! Aurora is also waiting for her turn so now give her the bold brown eye shadow and select the nude lips for the girl. She would look pretty in a blue top combined with a cute pair of green leggings and a khaki knitted sweater. Do not forget to finalize her look with the girly-girl accessories like a chic pink handbag. Wow! These two pretties are now ready to go outside for a memorable hangout. Find some extra fun in our more popular titles from the category of free girls games and have a blast, no download required!
